{"tid":2260289,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★BitCoin--女投資者千個幣在冷錢包消失","createTime":"2020-10-27T12:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T13:06:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f62e96cc4e1ba23f22fcfc492788d8ea003bec2d","tid":2260289,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:56:33.000Z","msg":"事主熱錢包內有1500個比特幣<br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳辭指，事主早於2013年開始投資比特幣，翌年10月已有1500個比特幣，<a href=\"http://並將之保存在虛擬貨幣交易平台Blockchain.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%A6%E5%B0%87%E4%B9%8B%E4%BF%9D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0Blockchain.com&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDAjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=5bfbeb7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">並將之保存在虛擬貨幣交易平台Blockchain.com</a>所開的熱錢包內。<br />\n<br />\n2017年中旬，事主計劃賣出比特幣，於Bitcoinnect Group（比特通集團有限公司）的交易平台Bitfirst放售，但由於該平台停止運作，遂轉用另一平台Blcex。據其理解，被告是「比特通」及Blcex的行政總裁。<br />\n<br />\n講座認識被告求幫助交易<br />\n<br />\n事主及後發現放售需時，有次在某講座中認識被告後，便叫被告幫忙，交易最終成功完成，兩人自此繼續聯繫。被告建議做中介助事主在場外作比特幣交易，並收取2%交易額作佣金。<br />\n<br />\n被告提議事主訂購冷錢包<br />\n<br />\n2018年1月，被告幫事主處理比特幣交易，期間稱事主比特幣數量多，存於熱錢包內並不安全，提議幫她訂購冷錢包。<br />\n<br />\n同年3月，事主讓被告在其手提電腦安裝登入帳戶及密碼，被告將3個Trezor冷錢包交予事主，並強調均未開封。他在事主同意下，替事主在手提電腦安裝其中一個，之後叫她設密碼，又著她抄下24組回復字。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/541128/%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E9%A8%99%E6%A1%88-%E5%A5%B3%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E5%8D%83%E5%80%8B%E5%B9%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%86%B7%E9%8C%A2%E5%8C%85%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1-%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E9%80%9A%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E6%B6%89%E6%AC%BA%E8%A9%90%E5%8F%97%E5%AF%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F541128%2F%25E6%25AF%2594%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E9%25A8%2599%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%2586%25B7%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1-%25E6%25AF%2594%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25A3%2581%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E8%25A9%2590%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AF%25A9&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDAjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=3879d61f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/541128/%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E9%A8%99%E6%A1%88-%E5%A5%B3%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E5%8D%83%E5%80%8B%E5%B9%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%86%B7%E9%8C%A2%E5%8C%85%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1-%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E9%80%9A%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E6%B6%89%E6%AC%BA%E8%A9%90%E5%8F%97%E5%AF%A9</a>"},{"pid":"960442f40c82522f1c54e5234a2add7fef9555e9","tid":2260289,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"Hang機----&gt;Reset<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4124372fccf39ab762b6c5d2efa905bd7b5da2e","tid":2260289,"uid":27362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b990c2788737013b5f98f313943b72a3914f5623","tid":2260289,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70130ca6b3979c99be5052536d9d6e6cb4fc2855","tid":2260289,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"如果佢心雄無take profit <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以斬掉重練了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96e524efba177c72099b55d6806bb27a9335183","tid":2260289,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"1500個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a30676e72cfccdc24df301c